Generate Missionary Submission File

Source: R/missionary.R
generate_missionary_submission_file.Rd

Generate Missionary Submission File

Usage

generate_missionary_submission_file(
  input_df = usheUtils::fake_mission_df,
  with_intermediates = FALSE
)

Arguments

input_df

A Data Frame. Must contain the following data fields: (last_name, first_name, middle_name, birth_date, term_end_date, student_id).

with_intermediates

Boolean: Option to include intermediate calculated fields.

Value

A Data Frame, with all of the USHE elements required for upload submission. This will also include intermediate values, used to calculate USHE data elements, if option is set.
